WAFER WORKS CORP (6182)  said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 51.36% to NT$202,109,000 from NT$415,556,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales            202,109          415,556    
YOY%             -51.36%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,158,797        4,694,056   
YOY%              9.90%  
=================================================================
 